===Etymology===
From Latin '''[[commissio]]''', ''sending together'' or ''commission'', from prefix '''[[com-]]''', ''with'', + noun of action '''[[missio]]''', ''sending'', from perfect passive participle '''[[missus]]''', ''sent'', from verb '''[[mitto|mittō]]''', ''send'', + noun of action suffix '''[[-io]]'''

